					<div class="et_pb_blurb_container">
						<h3 class="et_pb_module_header"><span>Academics</span></h3>
						<div class="et_pb_blurb_description"><p>Bridging theory and practice. ECBA connects scholars with leading practitioners to advance European criminal law.</p></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_blurb et_pb_blurb_5 et_clickable  et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_blurb_position_top et_pb_bg_layout_light">
				
				
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_blurb_content">
					<div class="et_pb_main_blurb_image"><span class="et_pb_image_wrap et_pb_only_image_mode_wrap"><img decoding="async" width="160" height="169" src="https://site.ecba.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ecba-leaf-w160-incl-zone-cream.png" alt="" class="et-waypoint et_pb_animation_top et_pb_animation_top_tablet et_pb_animation_top_phone wp-image-1352"></span></div>
					<div class="et_pb_blurb_container">
						<h3 class="et_pb_module_header"><span>Collective Members</span></h3>
						<div class="et_pb_blurb_description"><p>Strengthening the legal profession. ECBA equips lawyers and bar associations with tools, training, and cross-border legal support.</p></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_blurb et_pb_blurb_6 et_clickable  et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_blurb_position_top et_pb_bg_layout_light">
				
				
				
				
